KodaX Space is the Electron desktop client for the KodaX ecosystem
(see https://github.com/icetomoyo/KodaX). It consumes the public
`@kodax-ai/coding`, `@kodax-ai/llm`, `@kodax-ai/agent` and
`@kodax-ai/skills` SDK packages in-process, and ships independently
of any closed-source KodaX-private components.
